methods.name: public long getTimeSinceCreatedMillis()
methods.comment:
* Gets time since the corresponding log session is created in millisecond.
     * @return the timestamp since the instance is created, or -1 if unknown.
     * @see LogSessionId
     * @see PlaybackSession
     * @see RecordingSession

methods.name: public Bundle getMetricsBundle()
methods.comment:
* Gets metrics-related information that is not supported by dedicated methods. *

It is intended to be used for backwards compatibility by the metrics infrastructure.
